 with an excess in the N/He ratio\nin the N enriched area of the order of both, the atmospheric N/He ratios in WR\nstars and the uncertainties estimated for the N/He ratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2013 14:44:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 24 Mar 2013 20:52:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
